                        "displayName": "Valter Kungla",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I have simlar issue I can read form MS AS all other domains but not one.\r\nFor excample:\r\n$ldap->searchEntries('(objectclass=*)','DC=akadeemia,DC=erasise'); IS OK\r\n$ldap->searchEntries('(objectclass=*)','DC=klassid,DC=akadeemia,DC=erasise'); gives\r\n\r\n0xa (Referral; 0000202B: RefErr: DSID-031006BB, data 0, 1 access points ref 1: 'klassid.akadeemia.erasise' ): getting first entry\r\n\r\nI investicate it in my own too. I let you know if I find somethig",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=valter",
                        "name": "valter",
                        "displayName": "Valter Kungla",
