                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=antych",
                        "name": "antych",
                        "displayName": "Karol Grecki",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I upgraded from 1.9.4 to 1.10.1, LDAP auth stopped working. I applied version from trunk but it doesn't help. I run it through a debugger and it returns some error code = 49 and this \"0x31 (Invalid credentials; 80090308: LdapErr: DSID-0C090334, comment: AcceptSecurityContext error, data 525, vece)\"\r\nIt works fine when I go back to 1.9.4",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=antych",
                        "name": "antych",
                        "displayName": "Karol Grecki",
                        "active": true
